name: 「月相」-朔
background: This high-capacity portable W-Engine can collect dissipated energy from its surrounding, thus enhancing the combat effectiveness of its operator. It is a perfect choice for novice explorers who are worries that their W-Engine may run out of power during expeditions.
skill: Launching an EX Special Attack generates 3/3.5/4/4.5/5 Energy for the equipper. This effect can trigger once every 12s.
